node.text: “Thanks to everyone who came out to the FDMG Academy Campus in Wilmington(DE) yesterday to help us make history yesterday! I cannot believe what I saw yesterday, which I can only describe as “Absolutely Amazing!” You all showed up and showed out! You packed Ifatunde Avenue! You came from all over the country and world! The vendors, the chefs, the fashion show team, the performances, the fellowship and energy was beyond anything we could imagine! I didn’t realize how many of us were there until I took the stage to speak! To my 2021 FDMG Fest Organizing Team this could not have happpened without - Great Job! It was a lot of work but we did it, and we did it together! I cannot wait until next year’s festival so please mark your calendar for Saturday September 10th, 2022! Please hold onto your yellow wristbands and wear them next year for a special door prize raffle! The Ancestors blessed us yesterday! Please text, WhatsApp or email your FDMG Fest photos to Dr.Umar at 215-989-9858/DrUmarJohnson@Yahoo.com. Thank You! Thank You! Thank You!”
